WEBVTT

00:02.002 --> 00:03.104
HEY, BABY.
HEY.

00:03.104 --> 00:04.675
WHAT´S ALL THIS?

00:04.675 --> 00:07.178
OH, I TOOK ON A NEW SALES
TERRITORY, AND I´M SWAMPED.

00:07.178 --> 00:09.610
CAN YOU TAKE CARMEN OUT SATURDAY
FOR HER DRIVING LESSON?

00:09.610 --> 00:11.512
YOU REALLY WANT TO PUT
A 15-YEAR-OLD GIRL

00:11.512 --> 00:13.444
BEHIND THE WHEEL
OF A 4,000-POUND TRUCK?

00:13.444 --> 00:15.046
HEY, COME ON, ANGIE.

00:15.046 --> 00:17.148
CARMEN STILL GETS STARTLED
BY HER OWN HOOP EARRINGS.

00:18.389 --> 00:21.122
"WHO´S THAT?"
"WHAT DO YOU WANT?"

00:21.122 --> 00:23.094
"LEAVE ME ALONE!"

00:24.795 --> 00:27.598
SHE ACED THE WRITTEN PART
OF THE DRIVING TEST.

00:27.598 --> 00:29.800
LOOK, I DON´T CARE. I DON´T
THINK SHE´S READY TO DRIVE.

00:29.800 --> 00:31.232
CALIFORNIA DOES.

00:31.232 --> 00:33.264
THEY GAVE HER
A LEARNER´S PERMIT.

00:33.264 --> 00:34.635
IF I CARED ABOUT PERMITS,

00:34.635 --> 00:36.737
WE WOULDN´T HAVE
A SECOND FLOOR ON THIS HOUSE.

00:36.737 --> 00:38.539
MOM, DAD, GUESS WHAT --

00:38.539 --> 00:40.771
JASON WAS JUST NOMINATED
FOR PROM KING.

00:40.771 --> 00:42.443
OOH.

00:42.443 --> 00:45.146
I REMEMBER WHEN I WAS NOMINATED
FOR PROM QUEEN.

00:45.146 --> 00:47.278
I WAS A SHOO-IN
TILL I GOT THAT ZIT

00:47.278 --> 00:48.819
TWO DAYS BEFORE THE DANCE.

00:48.819 --> 00:50.681
I WITHDREW
FROM THE COMPETITION,

00:50.681 --> 00:53.224
BUT I STILL GOT SO MANY WRITE-IN
VOTES, I MADE RUNNER-UP.

00:53.224 --> 00:57.658
IN THE YEARBOOK, THEY CALLED ME
"THE PEOPLE´S PROM QUEEN."

00:57.658 --> 01:00.661
GLORY DAYS, HUH, BABY?
YEAH.

01:00.661 --> 01:05.266
OH, BEFORE JASON TAKES OFF,
CAN YOU GUYS SIGN THIS?

01:05.266 --> 01:08.299
ALLENDALE STARTED THIS WHOLE
CAMPAIGN ABOUT PROM THIS YEAR.

01:08.299 --> 01:10.141
IT´S "PROM-ISE TO BE SAFE."

01:10.141 --> 01:12.403
YEAH, THEY CAME UP WITH THESE
CONTRACTS WHERE STUDENTS PROMISE

01:12.403 --> 01:15.306
TO PRACTICE ABSTINENCE
AND SOBRIETY ON PROM NIGHT.

01:15.306 --> 01:17.148
WE´VE ALREADY SIGNED IT,

01:17.148 --> 01:19.150
AND WE´D LIKE YOU BOTH
TO SIGN IT, TOO.

01:19.150 --> 01:21.182
WHAT´S THE PENALTY
IF YOU BREAK THE CONTRACT?

01:21.182 --> 01:23.314
WELL, IT´S A MATTER
OF HONOR.

01:23.314 --> 01:26.417
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

01:26.417 --> 01:29.860
THEY´RE TRYING
TO BE RESPONSIBLE.

01:29.860 --> 01:32.263
ALL RIGHT, FINE,
I´LL SIGN IT.

01:32.263 --> 01:35.196
JUST NEED TO ADD
ONE LITTLE THING.

01:35.196 --> 01:39.630
"IF JASON McNAMARA, HENCEFORTH
REFERRED TO AS ´THE ACCUSED,´

01:39.630 --> 01:41.132
"VIOLATES THIS CONTRACT OR...

01:41.132 --> 01:42.133
"MY DAUGHTER,

01:43.834 --> 01:48.439
"I, GEORGE LOPEZ, HENCEFORTH
REFERRED TO AS ´THE CASTRATOR,´

01:48.439 --> 01:54.585
WILL KNOWINGLY, WILLFULLY,
AND THOROUGHLY BEAT YOU DOWN."

01:54.585 --> 01:56.787
I JUST NEED YOU
TO INITIAL RIGHT THERE

01:56.787 --> 01:58.449
WHERE IT SAYS "BEAT YOU DOWN."

01:58.449 --> 02:00.321
GIVE ME THAT.

02:02.323 --> 02:05.256
WOULDN´T IT BE GREAT
IF EVERY STUDENT SIGNED
A CONTRACT LIKE THIS?

02:05.256 --> 02:07.398
YEAH, BUT SINCE THEY WON´T,
THERE´S GOING TO BE

02:07.398 --> 02:09.760
A LOT OF DRUNK DRIVERS
OUT ON THE ROAD THAT NIGHT.

02:09.760 --> 02:11.662
YOU KNOW
WHAT WOULD BE SMART?

02:11.662 --> 02:13.264
WE SHOULD RENT A HOTEL ROOM

02:13.264 --> 02:15.406
WITH A BUNCH OF OUR FRIENDS,
AND THEN AFTER PROM,

02:15.406 --> 02:17.708
WE COULD HANG OUT THERE
UNTIL IT´S SAFE.

02:17.708 --> 02:21.272
ISN´T IT GREAT? IT´S JUST,
LIKE, COMING TO ME NOW.

02:21.272 --> 02:22.773
I GOT A BETTER IDEA.

02:22.773 --> 02:25.376
HOW ABOUT YOU
DON´T GO TO THE HOTEL,

02:25.376 --> 02:28.279
YOU´RE HOME BY MIDNIGHT
OR YOU´RE GROUNDED FOR A YEAR?

02:28.279 --> 02:28.919
YEAH.

02:28.919 --> 02:30.651
ISN´T THAT GREAT?

02:30.651 --> 02:33.284
OH, MY GOD, IT´S ALL JUST
COMING TO ME NOW. OH, GOD.

02:33.284 --> 02:35.686
BUT, DAD, WE PROMISED
NOTHING WOULD HAPPEN,

02:35.686 --> 02:37.358
AND WE EVEN SIGNED
A CONTRACT.

02:37.358 --> 02:39.330
THAT WAS GOOD ENOUGH
FOR ALL THE OTHER PARENTS.

02:39.330 --> 02:41.232
WE DON´T CARE
ABOUT THE OTHER PARENTS.

02:41.232 --> 02:42.663
YOU´RE NOT STAYING
IN A HOTEL.

02:42.663 --> 02:44.495
WELL, JASON AND I
ARE ALONE ALL THE TIME.

02:44.495 --> 02:47.238
IF WE WANTED TO HAVE SEX,
WE WOULD HAVE DONE IT ALREADY.

02:47.238 --> 02:48.639
HE HAS A VAN.

02:48.639 --> 02:50.501
WE COULD HAVE DONE IT RIGHT
BEFORE WE CAME HERE.

02:50.501 --> 02:52.703
MAYBE WE DID.
CARMEN.

02:54.505 --> 02:57.448
THE BEAT-DOWN CLAUSE.

02:57.448 --> 03:00.211
YOU´RE 15 YEARS OLD,
AND YOU´RE A SOPHOMORE, OKAY?

03:00.211 --> 03:01.752
YOU´RE LUCKY WE´RE LETTING YOU
GO TO THE PROM.

03:01.752 --> 03:03.354
I DIDN´T GO TO MY PROM.

03:03.354 --> 03:05.486
THAT´S ´CAUSE
YOU WERE WAY OUT OF YOUR LEAGUE.

03:05.486 --> 03:07.758
YOU WERE A FIVE, CHATO.

03:09.420 --> 03:12.593
AND YOU WERE ASKING OUT
EIGHTS AND NINES.

03:12.593 --> 03:15.626
YOU GOTTA AIM LOWER.

03:15.626 --> 03:17.568
SIX.

03:17.568 --> 03:19.230
10.

03:20.771 --> 03:22.633
I´LL SEE YOU LATER, CARMEN.

03:22.633 --> 03:24.635
BYE, JASON.

03:24.635 --> 03:27.778
MR. LOPEZ,
YOU´RE NOT A FIVE.

03:27.778 --> 03:29.740
YOU´RE A NINE.

03:29.740 --> 03:32.613
YOU´RE NOT STAYING
IN A HOTEL.

03:32.613 --> 03:34.245
LATER, FOUR.

03:35.916 --> 03:37.518
I´M READY, GRANDMA.

03:37.518 --> 03:40.651
OKAY. I´M TAKING MAX
TO THE ARCADE AT THE MALL.

03:40.651 --> 03:42.253
OH, CAN I HAVE A RIDE?

03:42.253 --> 03:43.924
I WANT TO START LOOKING
FOR PROM DRESSES.

03:43.924 --> 03:45.756
UNLESS I´M TOO YOUNG
TO WEAR A DRESS

03:45.756 --> 03:47.558
AND I SHOULD GO TO THE PROM
IN A ONESIE.

03:47.558 --> 03:49.430
YOU´D LIKE THAT,
WOULDN´T YOU?

03:49.430 --> 03:51.302
SNAPS AT THE CROTCH --
I DON´T THINK SO.

03:51.302 --> 03:54.305
GRANDMA, HOW LATE WERE YOU OUT
ON PROM NIGHT?

03:54.305 --> 03:56.637
OOH, I THINK I CRAWLED HOME

03:56.637 --> 03:58.569
´BOUT 5:00 OR 6:00
IN THE MORNING.

03:58.569 --> 04:00.240
DID YOU HEAR THAT, DAD?

04:00.240 --> 04:02.443
YEAH, MOM, TELL HER
WHAT YOU WERE DOING.

04:02.443 --> 04:04.875
I WORKED A DOUBLE SHIFT
AT THE FACTORY,

04:04.875 --> 04:07.017
THEN I WENT TO THIRSTY´S,

04:07.017 --> 04:09.680
AND THEN I WENT HOME
TO BREAST-FEED YOUR FATHER.

04:09.680 --> 04:11.922
YOU NEVER BREAST-FED ME.

04:19.730 --> 04:21.832
WONDER WHO THAT WAS.

04:23.634 --> 04:26.266
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

04:36.907 --> 04:42.413
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

05:13.744 --> 05:14.945
AFTERNOON.

05:15.986 --> 05:17.448
ARE YOU GEORGE LOPEZ?

05:17.448 --> 05:19.620
NO, OFFICER, I´M JIM WILLIAMS.

05:19.620 --> 05:22.052
MY WIFE AND I JUST MOVED HERE
FROM SALT LAKE.

05:22.052 --> 05:23.494
I SELL LUMBER.

05:23.494 --> 05:25.926
ARE THESE YOUR CHILDREN?

05:25.926 --> 05:28.459
NO, MY WIFE, DEBBIE,
IS BARREN.

05:28.459 --> 05:30.361
CARMEN, MAX,
ARE YOU OKAY?

05:30.361 --> 05:32.062
OFFICER, WHAT HAPPENED?

05:32.062 --> 05:33.664
THIS ONE WAS DRIVING,

05:33.664 --> 05:36.437
THIS ONE WASN´T WEARING
HIS SEAT BELT,

05:36.437 --> 05:38.539
AND THIS ONE HAD AN EXPIRED
REGISTRATION

05:38.539 --> 05:40.671
AND AN OPEN BEER
IN THE CAR.

05:40.671 --> 05:43.444
I DON´T WANT TO TELL YOU
HOW TO DO YOUR JOB, MAN,

05:43.444 --> 05:46.016
BUT SHOULDN´T
THAT ONE BE CUFFED?

05:46.016 --> 05:49.119
I´M GOING TO RELEASE
THE MINORS INTO YOUR CUSTODY.

05:49.119 --> 05:50.881
BUT YOU´VE GOT
A DATE IN COURT.

05:50.881 --> 05:52.523
OH, GOOD JOB, OFFICER.

05:52.523 --> 05:55.486
YOU STOPPED A LITTLE OLD LADY
FROM SIPPING A BEER.

05:55.486 --> 05:57.728
YOU KNOW, WHY DON´T YOU GO
TO A CRACK HOUSE

05:57.728 --> 06:00.631
AND MAKE SURE THEY´RE REWINDING
THEIR VIDEOS?

06:00.631 --> 06:04.495
IT´S GOING TO BE A PLEASURE
TESTIFYING AGAINST YOU, MA´AM.

06:04.495 --> 06:06.497
YOU KNOW WHAT --
MOM!

06:08.399 --> 06:10.100
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?
WHERE IS YOUR JUDGMENT?

06:10.100 --> 06:13.373
HOW COULD YOU DRINK
WITH A 15-YEAR-OLD GIRL
BEHIND THE WHEEL?

06:13.373 --> 06:15.506
COME ON.
I WAS CHOKING ON A FRENCH FRY,

06:15.506 --> 06:17.478
AND THERE WAS NOTHING ELSE
TO DRINK!

06:17.478 --> 06:18.849
IT WAS JUST ONE SIP.

06:18.849 --> 06:21.381
GEORGE, COME ON.
YOU OF ALL PEOPLE KNOW

06:21.381 --> 06:23.784
THAT I CAN DRINK A BEER
AND WATCH A KID.

06:23.784 --> 06:25.886
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
YOU NEVER WATCHED ME.

06:25.886 --> 06:27.918
THE NEIGHBORS HAD TO PITCH IN
TO BUILD A FENCE

06:27.918 --> 06:30.390
TO KEEP ME FROM CRAWLING
IN THE STREET!

06:31.922 --> 06:35.566
CARMEN, WE NEVER GAVE YOU
PERMISSION TO DRIVE WITH BENNY.

06:35.566 --> 06:37.428
I KNOW THAT,
BUT I´VE GOT MY PERMIT,

06:37.428 --> 06:39.470
AND I WANT TO GET MY LICENSE
IN SIX MONTHS.

06:39.470 --> 06:41.131
SOMEONE´S GOTTA TEACH ME
HOW TO DRIVE,

06:41.131 --> 06:42.673
AND YOU NEVER HAVE THE TIME.

06:42.673 --> 06:44.535
HONEY, I WOULD LOVE
TO DO IT,

06:44.535 --> 06:46.677
BUT WORK IS REALLY BUSY
FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

06:46.677 --> 06:48.539
CAN YOU TAKE HER OUT
THIS WEEK?

06:48.539 --> 06:50.080
I DON´T KNOW...

06:50.080 --> 06:52.443
PLEASE, DADDY, PLEASE?

06:52.443 --> 06:55.546
COME ON, HONEY.

06:55.546 --> 06:57.918
YOU ARE THE BEST DRIVER
IN THE FAMILY.

06:57.918 --> 07:00.551
I KNOW I´M THE BEST.

07:01.852 --> 07:03.854
ALL RIGHT, I´LL DO IT.

07:03.854 --> 07:05.155
[ SQUEALS ]

07:05.155 --> 07:07.458
HAVE JASON DROP YOU OFF
ON FRIDAY AFTER WORK.

07:07.458 --> 07:08.929
THANK YOU,
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

07:08.929 --> 07:10.931
♫ I´M GETTING MY LICENSE ♫

07:10.931 --> 07:12.463
♫ I´M GOING DRIVING ♫

07:12.463 --> 07:14.104
OKAY, NOW,
IF YOU HAD DONE THAT

07:14.104 --> 07:16.967
WHEN THE COP PULLED US OVER,
I WOULD STILL HAVE MY CAR.

07:21.972 --> 07:24.775
LISTEN UP, EVERYBODY.

07:24.775 --> 07:28.018
AS YOU KNOW, THIS AFTERNOON,
MY MOTHER HAD A COURT DATE.

07:28.018 --> 07:32.483
THE JUDGE WANTED
TO TEACH HER A LESSON...

07:32.483 --> 07:35.726
SO HE SENTENCED HER
TO PUBLIC HUMILIATION.

07:35.726 --> 07:37.588
NOW, I DON´T WANT ANYONE

07:37.588 --> 07:40.130
TO BE SCARED BY WHAT
I´M ABOUT TO SAY --

07:40.130 --> 07:42.563
MOM, TAKE IT OFF.

07:48.138 --> 07:51.842
"ASK ME HOW I ENDANGERED
MY GRANDCHILDREN´S LIVES."

07:51.842 --> 07:54.505
TURN AROUND SO I CAN SEE
THE ANSWER.

07:56.206 --> 07:59.209
BEND OVER.
I´LL GIVE IT TO YOU.

08:00.951 --> 08:04.815
NOW, IF ANYONE SEES MY MOTHER
WITHOUT THIS SIGN,

08:04.815 --> 08:08.488
REPORT IT TO ME
BECAUSE SHE COULD GO TO JAIL.

08:08.488 --> 08:10.691
NONE OF US WANT THAT, RIGHT?
[ LAUGHS ]

08:13.223 --> 08:16.026
HEY, DADDY, I´M READY
FOR MY DRIVING LESSON.

08:16.026 --> 08:17.628
OH, OKAY.

08:17.628 --> 08:20.631
OH, I JUST GOT ONE THING
TO TAKE CARE OF, CARMEN.

08:22.533 --> 08:25.035
I´M GOING DRIVING
WITH CARMEN.

08:30.611 --> 08:32.182
[ BOTH SNIFFLE ]

08:32.182 --> 08:33.584
I LOVE YOU, MAN.

08:33.584 --> 08:35.145
DON´T FORGET ME.

08:35.145 --> 08:36.587
I WON´T.

08:36.587 --> 08:38.188
AND YOU GOT MY WORD.

08:38.188 --> 08:41.652
I´M GOING TO WAIT AT LEAST
ONE YEAR TILL I ASK ANGIE OUT.

08:45.525 --> 08:46.997
OKAY, TURN THE CAR ON.

08:49.630 --> 08:51.732
OKAY, MAKE SURE
THE EMERGENCY BRAKE IS OFF,

08:51.732 --> 08:53.864
AND CHECK YOUR MIRRORS.

08:53.864 --> 08:56.536
MM. I CAN´T SEE OUT
MY SIDE MIRROR.

08:56.536 --> 08:57.938
THERE´S AN OBSTRUCTION

08:57.938 --> 09:00.671
ABOUT TWO TIMES THE SIZE
OF A NORMAL HUMAN HEAD.

09:03.013 --> 09:05.616
THANK YOU.

09:05.616 --> 09:09.019
OKAY, CHECK FOR TRAFFIC,
USE YOUR SIGNAL...

09:09.019 --> 09:10.821
AND EASE ONTO THE ROAD.

09:13.654 --> 09:15.886
SHOULD I GO
THE USUAL WAY HOME?

09:15.886 --> 09:17.087
NO, I WANT TO GO
DOWN VAN NUYS,

09:17.087 --> 09:19.559
ACROSS MAGNOLIA,
THEN UP RESEDA.

09:19.559 --> 09:22.963
OH, THAT´S COOL. WE´RE
TAKING THE MAJOR STREETS SO
I CAN PRACTICE PASSING.

09:22.963 --> 09:25.235
NO, THAT WAY WE PASS
THREE HOSPITALS AND A CHURCH

09:25.235 --> 09:28.268
IN CASE I NEED LAST RITES.

09:28.268 --> 09:30.841
MAN, I CAN´T WAIT
UNTIL I GET MY LICENSE.

09:30.841 --> 09:32.943
THEN I CAN DRIVE MYSELF
OVER TO JASON´S

09:32.943 --> 09:34.845
AND TO THE MALL
AND SCHOOL AND WORK.

09:34.845 --> 09:37.107
YEAH, I WON´T NEED YOU
FOR ANY OF THAT ANYMORE.

09:37.107 --> 09:39.610
WELL, THAT´S ASSUMING
YOU PASS YOUR DRIVER´S TEST.

09:39.610 --> 09:40.981
I´M PASSING THAT TEST.

09:40.981 --> 09:42.713
IT´S MY TICKET TO FREEDOM.

09:42.713 --> 09:44.715
TO GET OUT OF THAT HOUSE
AND JUST GO SOMEWHERE

09:44.715 --> 09:46.787
WHERE I´M NOT BEING WATCHED OVER
LIKE A PRISONER

09:46.787 --> 09:48.959
BY TWO CANNIBALS
OF THE HUMAN SPIRIT.

09:50.290 --> 09:53.023
I MEAN, YOU KNOW,
THANKS FOR EVERYTHING.

09:53.023 --> 09:55.265
OKAY, EASE UP. YOU´RE GETTING
TOO CLOSE TO THAT CAR.

09:55.265 --> 09:56.827
I WAS GOING TO PASS HIM.

09:56.827 --> 09:58.598
WELL, THEN, YOU SHOULD HAVE
SIGNALED 100 FEET AGO.

09:58.598 --> 10:00.130
I´LL SIGNAL NOW.

10:00.130 --> 10:02.372
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
CHECKED MY MIRRORS
AND SIGNALED.

10:02.372 --> 10:04.735
BUT YOU DIDN´T CHECK
YOUR BLIND SPOT.
WHERE´S MY BLIND SPOT?

10:04.735 --> 10:06.777
YOU CAN´T SEE IT!
OKAY!

10:06.777 --> 10:08.138
GOD, WOULD YOU STOP
YELLING AT ME?

10:08.138 --> 10:09.880
YOU´RE MAKING ME
ALL NERVOUS.

10:09.880 --> 10:11.812
YOU´RE GOING OVER
A DOUBLE YELLOW LINE, CARMEN.

10:11.812 --> 10:13.043
PLEASE STOP IT.

10:13.043 --> 10:15.045
PAY ATTENTION
OR YOU ARE GOING TO KILL US.

10:15.045 --> 10:17.147
I DON´T WANT
TO DO THIS ANYMORE.
OKAY, THEN PULL OVER.

10:17.147 --> 10:18.949
OKAY.
WATCH OUT!

10:18.949 --> 10:20.020
AHH!

10:21.752 --> 10:22.953
OH, MY GOD.

10:22.953 --> 10:25.355
BABY, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
I THINK SO.

10:25.355 --> 10:28.198
NOT YOU, MY TRUCK.

10:28.198 --> 10:32.062
BABY, TALK TO DADDY.
I´LL GET YOU SOME HELP.

10:36.907 --> 10:40.410
WHATEVER HE SAYS,
IT WASN´T MY FAULT.

10:40.410 --> 10:42.342
WHAT HAPPENED?

10:42.342 --> 10:43.914
DID YOU HIT SOMETHING?

10:43.914 --> 10:46.346
DO WE NEED TO WASH THE CAR
OR BURY ANYTHING?

10:48.278 --> 10:49.820
WHAT AM I SAYING?

10:49.820 --> 10:51.381
YOU WERE HERE ALL NIGHT,
WE PLAYED CHARADES,

10:51.381 --> 10:54.885
YOU GOT STUCK ON "STAR WARS,"
AND WE ALL LAUGHED.

10:54.885 --> 10:57.257
CARMEN WASN´T
PAYING ATTENTION.

10:57.257 --> 11:00.390
SHE CUT ACROSS TWO LANES
OF TRAFFIC AND WENT UP A CURB!

11:00.390 --> 11:02.232
HEY, I WAS PAYING ATTENTION.

11:02.232 --> 11:04.865
YOU JUST KEPT YELLING AT ME
AND MAKING ME ALL NERVOUS.

11:04.865 --> 11:06.737
AM I MAKING YOU
NERVOUS NOW?

11:06.737 --> 11:10.340
I KNOW YOU´RE ONLY STAYING
WITH HIM FOR THE KIDS,

11:10.340 --> 11:13.173
BUT WE DON´T
WANT HIM ANYMORE.

11:14.875 --> 11:16.406
WHAT HAPPENED OUT THERE?

11:16.406 --> 11:19.449
ANGIE, SHE CAN´T FOCUS.
SHE´S A HORRIBLE DRIVER.

11:19.449 --> 11:22.753
I TOOK HER OUT DRIVING LAST
SATURDAY, AND SHE WAS JUST FINE.

11:22.753 --> 11:25.185
YEAH, WERE YOU FOCUSING, OR
WERE YOU PUCKERING AND GLOSSING?

11:25.185 --> 11:27.217
´CAUSE I´VE SEEN
YOU DRIVE LIKE THAT.

11:33.463 --> 11:35.766
DO YOU WANT A TALK
OR A FIGHT?

11:35.766 --> 11:38.028
I DON´T CARE. I´LL FIGHT
BECAUSE YOU KNOW WHAT?

11:38.028 --> 11:40.170
I JUST CHEATED DEATH.
I FEEL ALIVE!

11:41.431 --> 11:44.775
BUT IF YOU WANT TO TALK,
THAT´S OKAY, TOO.

11:44.775 --> 11:47.908
YELLING IS NOT GOING TO MAKE HER
A BETTER DRIVER.

11:47.908 --> 11:49.780
LOOK, ANGIE,
I HAVE TO YELL AT HER.

11:49.780 --> 11:51.782
DO YOU KNOW HOW DANGEROUS
IT IS OUT THERE?

11:51.782 --> 11:53.784
SHE´S TOO COCKY.
SHE THINKS SHE KNOWS IT ALL!

11:53.784 --> 11:55.786
SHE THINKS SHE´S GOING
TO BE ABLE TO DRIVE TO SCHOOL

11:55.786 --> 11:58.048
AND TO JASON´S HOUSE
LIKE IT´S NO BIG DEAL!

11:58.048 --> 11:59.850
I THINK SHE CAN HANDLE THAT.

11:59.850 --> 12:01.721
NOT IF SHE WON´T LISTEN.

12:01.721 --> 12:03.353
SHE´S TOO EMOTIONAL.

12:03.353 --> 12:05.826
I SAY ONE LITTLE THING,
IT´S "I HATE YOU!"

12:05.826 --> 12:07.057
STOMP, STOMP, SLAM!

12:07.057 --> 12:09.930
"YOU´RE THE WORST DAD EVER!"

12:09.930 --> 12:12.002
STOMP, STOMP, SLAM!

12:12.002 --> 12:14.104
"NOBODY CARES
ABOUT MY FEELINGS!"

12:14.104 --> 12:16.406
STOMP, TRIP, FALL.

12:16.406 --> 12:20.040
MAYBE THE PROBLEM´S NOT HER,
IT´S YOU.

12:20.040 --> 12:22.042
YOU´RE BEING TOO IMPATIENT.

12:22.042 --> 12:24.074
I´M NOT IMPATIENT.

12:24.074 --> 12:25.946
YOU KNOW WHAT?
THIS IS NOT GOING TO WORK.

12:25.946 --> 12:28.418
I´LL JUST TEACH CARMEN ´ CAUSE
